   7              	@----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   8              	@----------------------------------SYMBOLIC VARIABLES------------------------------
   9              	@----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  10              	@Definition of symbolic variables associated with the memory regions of the three Keccak state shar
  11              	@Lane naming convention: A<x><y><m>_s<n>
  12              	@  <x> = row (b=0, g=1, k=2, m=3, s=4)
  13              	@  <y> = column (a=0, e=1, i=2, o=3, u=4)
  14              	@  <m> = lane half (0=low/even, 1=high/odd)
  15              	@  <n> = share index (0,1,2)
  16              	
